                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850112-85-victim852 t17850112-85-viclabel437"></join>, that he was then engaged with Captain Rogers, to go on a voyage in the Austrian, East Indiaman, as the Captain's steward; and did then and there, falsly and designedly, ask him to lend him his watch, that he might appear like a gentleman as he used to do, and would afterwards return the said watch, to the said 
